### Send mock email notification
POST http://localhost:8084/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "user-1",
  "recipient": "asha.rao@example.com",
  "subject": "SkyWays booking confirmed",
  "body": "Your SkyWays booking has been confirmed. Thank you for flying with us."
}

### Trigger mock email failure
POST http://localhost:8084/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "user-1",
  "recipient": "customer@fail.test",
  "subject": "SkyWays booking confirmed",
  "body": "This request simulates SendGrid rejection."
}

### Get one notification
GET http://localhost:8084/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}

### Get notifications for booking
GET http://localhost:8084/api/notifications?bookingId={{bookingId}}

### Get notifications for user
GET http://localhost:8084/api/notifications?userId=user-1
